{"lastModified":1764164687891,"uri":"c::7580644256::vessel::100f3f50-42a0-11ef-b99a-65cef4489bbd","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Summer Operating Area: USA - New England\nWinter Operating Area: Bahamas, USA - Florida\n\nCHARTER IN THE BAHAMAS THIS WINTER ABOARD M/Y INDY\n\nWelcome aboard INDY, where elegant styling, luxurious accommodations, and impressive performance await you. Fresh from a 2023 refit by acclaimed interior designer Patrick Knowles, INDY seamlessly blends luxury and comfort, making it the perfect charter choice. With a cruising speed of 19 knots and a top speed of 25 knots, INDY promises swift and stylish journeys. Its 21.3-foot beam, comparable to that of most 90-foot yachts, offering expansive space, while the solid fiberglass hull ensures exceptional strength and durability. INDY accommodates eight guests in four spacious cabins, along with a crew of four.\n\nThe expansive main salon on INDY features custom furnishings and a formal dining area with a custom-designed marble table and luxurious chairs. Start your day here with a tailor-made breakfast spread or unwind in the evening with a drink from the full bar while lounging on the sofa. INDY’s galley and seating area are equipped with all the necessities to create delicious meals while underway and can be closed off for extra privacy. Entertainment possibilities abound with the aft deck’s U-shaped sofa for alfresco dining, the aft flybridge’s grill, lounging chairs, and the perfect settee for enjoying sunset beverages and canopies. The enclosed flybridge is ideal for watching the horizon in complete comfort, featuring two sofas, a 2nd bar, and a pop-up TV.\n\nINDY’s full-beam master suite includes a king-size bed and lounge area, with an ensuite equipped with His and Hers entryways and an oversized shower. The VIP stateroom and guest cabins are equally luxurious, ensuring all guests enjoy complete comfort and privacy. Additional features include Smart TVs, dedicated ensuites, and lavishly appointed guest robes in all cabins.\n\nAn extended hydraulic swim platform, 76 inch tall ceilings and Naiad stabilizers complete INDY’s impressive charter profile, with a professional crew ready to cater to your needs at a moment’s notice.\n\n","blueprint":{"name":"INDY","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::100f3f50-42a0-11ef-b99a-65cef4489bbd::assets::51d62da0-ed67-11ef-8d19-533fcd37cf78/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::100f3f50-42a0-11ef-b99a-65cef4489bbd::assets::51b5d460-ed67-11ef-8d19-533fcd37cf78/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::100f3f50-42a0-11ef-b99a-65cef4489bbd::assets::51da7360-ed67-11ef-8d19-533fcd37cf78/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::100f3f50-42a0-11ef-b99a-65cef4489bbd::assets::51dbd2f0-ed67-11ef-8d1a-533fcd37cf78/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::100f3f50-42a0-11ef-b99a-65cef4489bbd::assets::51dae890-ed67-11ef-8d19-533fcd37cf78/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::100f3f50-42a0-11ef-b99a-65cef4489bbd::assets::51dc4820-ed67-11ef-8d1a-533fcd37cf78/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::100f3f50-42a0-11ef-b99a-65cef4489bbd::assets::51b38a70-ed67-11ef-8d19-533fcd37cf78/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::100f3f50-42a0-11ef-b99a-65cef4489bbd::assets::519f8d40-ed67-11ef-8d19-533fcd37cf78/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::100f3f50-42a0-11ef-b99a-65cef4489bbd::assets::51c7d5c0-ed67-11ef-8d19-533fcd37cf78/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::100f3f50-42a0-11ef-b99a-65cef4489bbd::assets::51d7db50-ed67-11ef-8d19-533fcd37cf78/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::100f3f50-42a0-11ef-b99a-65cef4489bbd::assets::51d961f0-ed67-11ef-8d19-533fcd37cf78/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::100f3f50-42a0-11ef-b99a-65cef4489bbd::assets::51da2540-ed67-11ef-8d19-533fcd37cf78/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::100f3f50-42a0-11ef-b99a-65cef4489bbd::assets::51d6c9e0-ed67-11ef-8d19-533fcd37cf78/{imageVariant}","